SELECT
	log_bpjs_id,
	jenis_transaksi,
	aksi,
	request_json,
	response_json,
	status_transaksi,
	http_status_code,
	error_code,
	error_message,
	endpoint_url,
	method,
	response_time_ms,
	is_deleted,
	deleted_at,
	deleted_by,
	created_by,
	created_at,
	updated_by,
	updated_at,
	no_bpjs
FROM
	"public".log_bpjs
name: public.log_bpjs
